    <div class="letter-body">
      <p>Time flies like crazy, I remember the first time we met, and I want to thank Discord for that, I still remember like it was yesterday, I was depressed I was trying to make friends and one day you appeared, it made me happy that I'm finally able to talk freely with someone, the friends I made during 11th and 12th weren't that great but they were good people, It's just that they betrayed me at some point, but you were there to listen, even though I didn't talk that much, but I still appreciated it, we spent days chatting, one thing led to another, and you confessed your feelings for me, I was really confused and happy and it made my day, and after that you went through a lot, I feel bad because I wasn't there when you needed me, it felt like the world was against us lol, we had our ups and downs, I still remember people tried to fix our relationship, and it somehow worked out, and I'm grateful that I've good friends, they help me a lot, sometimes I feel like I'm useless because I can't find a way to repay them.</p>
      <p>That was all about me, now let's get back to the topic, I know that you've gone through a lot of things, and I do know that many things have been bothering you, just don't forget that I'm here to listen everything, feel free to talk about anything, I wasn't able to talk properly because of my health condition, don't worry I'm alright for now, just make sure that you don't lose focus of your goals, don't let anyone get in the way, I know it sounds absurd, but you get it. I've been dreaming of meeting you one day, and I will try my best from now on to be the kind of person whom you can rely on, because you helped me a lot, you might not know it but I do, and I want to apologize because I've been rude, no wonder you call me Mr. Cold lol, I'll try to be a better person, because you deserve the best, that wasn't much but I do hope you like this small present, and yeah have a wonderful day. I love you <3 cuz you are the best.</p>
